%N A054532 Ramanujan sum T(n, k) = c_k(n) = Sum_{m=1..k, (m,k)=1} exp(2*Pi*i*m*n / k), triangular array read by rows for n >= 1 and 1 <= k <= n.
%C A054532 T(n, k) = c_k(n) = sum of the n-th powers of the k-th primitive roots of unity. - _Petros Hadjicostas_, Jul 27 2019
